description.plain:
The song ‘Voices in My Head’ is an unofficial Suicide Squad soundtrack mainly focusing on Harley Quinn and the fact that she has a condition where she hears voices in her head, possibly Schizophrenia.

It is also expressing that she is broken, she knows it and she likes herself that way even though others around her are trying to ‘fix’ her.
